<normalizedToken id="F2EEE6596ECA0C65F073194A7429CEB1" originalValue="Harin’Hala">Harin'Hala</normalizedToken>
, California Acad. of Sciences, Malaise, secondary tropical forest, MA-02-09C-61&quot; (CAS).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="89F2A30F48AC0C6F6C3AAD58AD3CB510" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" type="paratype">
<paragraph id="0EDE0C6E91C14E056163258075C3BAE2" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Paratype.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3EA49A0A182D169EB3A5E10CDFF879D9" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">
&quot;Madagascar, Fianarantsoa, Miandritsara Forest, 40 km S Ambositra, 
<geoCoordinate id="684F709E1EFCBBE6BE27334CC1702876" degrees="20" direction="south" minutes="47.56" orientation="latitude" precision="9" value="-20.792667">20°47.56'S</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="698F1F0B0F76F23C7A2774887E9DF768" degrees="47" direction="east" minutes="10.54" orientation="longitude" precision="9" value="47.175667">47°10.54'E</geoCoordinate>
